    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "An oval or circular structure equipped with tiered seating surrounding a central sandy area, where public spectacles were held in ancient Rome."
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Construcción oval o circular provista de un graderío alrededor de una zona arenosa central, en la que en la antigua Roma se celebraban espectáculos públicos."
