    "@value" : "Espacio destinado a la prestación de servicios orientados a la salud, el bienestar físico y mental y la relajación, mediante tratamientos, terapias o actividades especializadas"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Facility intended for the provision of services aimed at health, physical and mental well-being, and relaxation, through specialized treatments, therapies, or activities."
